description: Don Rafa Food Truck brings authentic Mexican food to the streets of Chicago. Don Rafa Restaurant is Chicago's Mexican communities best kept secret!Don Rafa/Sabas Vega Restaurant & Catering has created delicious meals for more than three generations. We are devoted to upholding the traditional flavors of our ancestors. In the early 1950’s we were the first establishment in Chicago to specialize in Carnitas. We guarantee every special event will be unforgettable by ensuring delicious Mexican cuisine.
name: Don Rafa
